We're looking for a Junior Backend Engineer with a focus on Flask/FastAPI to join our team. As a Junior Backend Engineer, you'll play a key role in building foundational components and integrating APIs. Collaborate with experienced engineers, contribute to bug resolution, and maintain clean, efficient code.

Job Descriptions:

Work collaboratively with team to develop and prototype Flask/FastAPI -based applications
Create simple technical documentation for functions/ API
Support the application in production
Requirements:

Fresh Graduate are welcome
Good Attitude
Good problem solving and logical thinking skills
Familiar with data structure and algorithm
Familiar writing with Python
Familiar with  Flask/FastAPI
Familiar with MySQL / PostgreQL
Familiar with RESTful API
Willingness to learn new skills
